#: ../../L/link-dead.rst:5
msgid "link-dead"
msgstr "link-dead"

#: ../../L/link-dead.rst:7
msgid "adj\\."
msgstr "形容詞"

#: ../../L/link-dead.rst:9
msgid ""
"[MUD] The state a player is in when they kill their connection to a "
":ref:`MUD` without leaving it properly. The player is then commonly left as "
"a statue in the game, and is only removed after a certain period of time (an"
" hour on most MUDs). Used on :ref:`IRC` as well, although it is "
"inappropriate in that context. Compare :ref:`netdead`\\."
msgstr ""
"[MUD] プレイヤーが\\ :ref:`MUD`\\ "
"から正しく退出せずに接続を切ったときの状態。プレイヤーはその後、ゲーム内で像として残されるのが普通で、一定の時間(ほとんどのMUDでは一時間)が経って初めて取り除かれる。\\"
" :ref:`IRC`\\ でも使われるが、その文脈では不適切である。\\ :ref:`netdead`\\ と比較せよ。"
